title: Albania Banks Balance Sheet
description: Banks Balance Sheet in Albania increased to 1908628.40 ALL Million in September from 1903964.20 ALL Million in August of 2022. Banks Balance Sheet in Albania averaged 1106317.10 ALL Million from 2002 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1908628.40 ALL Million in September of 2022 and a record low of 340653.80 ALL Million in December of 2002. This page provides - Albania Banks Balance Sheet- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
